reviews.review_text:
Best sounding quality by far Some of the recordings and soundboards of this show are pretty dull or drown out certain members. But this matrix is a God-send! I love these Orpheum '76 shows and think they're among the best of the year, but until I discovered this recording it was hard to appreciate the beauty of this show. It's not the crispest sounding recording, but it's the best of what's available IMO (and I've sampled them all). Phil is my favorite member to listen to and he's all over this one!

All good things in all good times. Thanks for uploading!

-Scotty D
